    <string name="help_text">Hello blank fragment</string>
    <string name="help1">Click on the float action button (+) to go to the editor and there you are ready to open up the editor. Type the note title and note content in the space provided and the note is saved at the specified `auto save` time defined in the application setting. Also, you can explicitly click on any of the save buttons provided in the app to save your note. \n</string>
