    <string name="help4">The TRASHED NOTES can be found in the trash bin located in the navigation drawer.</string>
    <string name="help5">Wish to RESTORE a note from the trash bin? Click the note and select the appropriate option from the popup menu.</string>
    <string name="help6">To DELETE a note permanently, simply choose delete when prompted from the trash bin, or click on the `TRASH` icon located on the toolbar to `EMPTY` the trash at once.</string>
